{"tid":1473804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非】光復香港用鍵盤輸出革命！","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T11:33:37.000Z","uid":34777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48965578f612c9d0ea289361e6d87aa4ae3ee444","tid":1473804,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:08:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的，作為多日ig鍵盤戰士<br />\n發現好多真心膠，好多五毛但又好多真心聽人講野嘅大陸人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同佢地做輸出革命時 記得唔好講粗口！！！</span></span><br />\n唔好比位人入覺得香港人淨係識講粗口<br />\n可以參照下隔離po用官方式答/講真相<br />\n有啲人真係仲有得救 靠大家一齊幫手做輸出革命啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有得救例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvzVkac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvzVkac.png&h=efbb3d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗚謝：會員10hojai幫手<br />\n<br />\n救咗例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAaxnoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAaxnoB.jpg&h=3a36502a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心膠例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U05Nbg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU05Nbg6.jpg&h=5769ed20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TnAhyvx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTnAhyvx.jpg&h=288d347a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ec24dvC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEc24dvC.jpg&h=bf9bd08a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢條友瘋狂侮辱義士，佢會遂個覆。為頭號難搞痴線佬，歡迎挑戰。住美國但撐中國有民主自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n五毛例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4r37bhB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4r37bhB.jpg&h=069b3eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非都做到嘅野 你唔係唔做下話？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 鍵盤革命！！！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1549b6094fc0281f76836a97571a87d8a7b116aa","tid":1473804,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"花木蘭支持香港警察濫用暴力及喬裝成示威者煽動並參與暴力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1473718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1473718</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n網戰啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62769f28f3277a17bf53264177b6ff1d0335bfca","tid":1473804,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"懷疑頭先開錯台 冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但真係好需要大家向支那做輸出革命架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多巴絲做到心灰 求下大家幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067217945248491c14fe4a61a963b99c0e775065","tid":1473804,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:13:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3ce8d84c4f6732b31de0ee9249d76eeef8f7ba7","tid":1473804,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f8b5fb979fd69e3d60e6362003f0e94575e5699","tid":1473804,"uid":94402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/face